Package: osfd
Title: Spatial Fisheries Data Tools
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Einar", "Hjorleifsson", , "einar.hjorleifsson@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A consolidation of functions used in the ICES WGSFD VMS and logbook
    data call workflow. Think of this as the junk drawer of spatial fisheries data
    processing — except organised, documented, and unlikely to fall on your foot.
